com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards
Class ToqNotification

java.lang.Object
  com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.ToqNotification
All Implemented Interfaces:
Parcelable
Direct Known Subclasses:
RemoteToqNotification
public class ToqNotification
extends Object
implements Parcelable

An abstract representation of a Toq notification which results in a pop-up on the Toq smartwatch. The notification pop-up is a rendering of a NotificationTextCard.

A notification is processed by the Toq smartwatch, which will determine whether to update a currently visible pop-up or launch a new pop-up depending on the Toq smartwatch's current state.

A specialised RemoteToqNotification implementation exists for use with the Toq app's API service.

Author:
mcaunter
See Also:
